data.description: Priced for a quick sale! This charming one-story home is located in the Caley Mill subdivision, which is known for its great location and good school district. The home offers a spacious open floor plan, with a living/dining room combo, breakfast area, and fireplace.  The home has three bedrooms and two bathrooms, all of which are located on the main level. The master bedroom has its own private bathroom.  The home also has a two-car garage and a large backyard, perfect for entertaining guests or letting the kids play.  This is a must-see for anyone looking for a charming and affordable home in a great location.
